This paper deals with the design of joint power and admission control algorithms for cellular networks, which is a topic related to networked systems (cs.NI) and information theory (cs.IT). The paper also discusses the prioritization of different tiers of cells, which is a topic related to control systems (cs.SY) and game theory (cs.GT). Finally, the paper proposes low-complexity algorithms for power update strategies, which is a topic related to multimedia (cs.MM) since efficient power allocation is important for multimedia applications.
